NOTE ON GAME ASSETS

The MIT license above covers ONLY the source code in this repository (the
asset decoders and the Android application). It does NOT cover any data or
artwork from Ultimate Soccer Manager 2, which is the intellectual property of
its respective rights holders (Impressions Software / Sierra On-Line and their
successors). No original game files, decoded databases, or artwork are
distributed in this repository. To build a complete game you must supply your
own legally-owned copy of Ultimate Soccer Manager 2 and run the decoders
locally. See README.md.
